Mouche Phillips https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mouche_Phillips 0 Mouche Phillips (born 23 March 1973 in Sydney, Australia) is an Australian actress, voice actress and theatre producer, best known for her television roles as Aviva "Viv" Newton in Home and Away (1989–90) and Eva Sykes in police procedural series Water Rats (2000–01).
